					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6146972#post-3838064</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6146972/avian-anthology-i#post-3838064</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 16 Jun 2018 20:24:13 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>TL333s</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1304786</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Now that its inception has been detailed, I think I finally understand what bothers me about this scenario (other than the interchangeability of birds with anything else, see also Beepocalypse).</p> <p>This is just a capricious god deciding to enact global change for&#8230; reasons. There was no warning. There was nothing anyone could do to stop it. There's probably nothing that can be done to reverse it.</p> <p>In the face of such omnipotent power, what's the point of even having a Foundation?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
