						 <p>A strong start to this two-parter. I love the characters here, and the dialog feels natural for each character. An excellent way of conveying the gravity of the situation without losing the humor inherent in it. If nothing else, this alone is truly the best place to start for those wanting to read everything Team Bird has been going for.</p> 
